    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3, a purist's specimen featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This naturally aspirated powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system to achieve a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a torque-sensing M-variable differential lock. The chassis integrity is superb, with a documented reinforced rear subframe and factory-spec bushings ensuring razor-sharp turn-in. This vehicle retains its original aerodynamic profile and staggered wheel fitment, representing a peak era of analog driver engagement.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
