      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car is in absolute mint condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with no swirl marks, stone chips, or blemishes of any kind. Every body panel is perfectly aligned with factory-spec gaps. Inside, the interior is flawless; the premium upholstery shows no signs of wear, the carpets are pristine, and all electronic components\u2014from the infotainment system to the climate control\u2014function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen rain or snow. A comprehensive service history is included, showing preventative maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. With low mileage and zero compromises, this vehicle offers a 'new car' experience for the most discerning enthusiast. It comes with all original keys, manuals, and a custom car cover.",
